title: Create a Story
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I am on the stories section of any of the above Forge Instances
WHEN: I select the "New" CTA
custom_expected: THEN: A new story should be successfully created

title: Add Video to Story
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I have create a story
WHEN: I attempt to add a video story part
custom_expected: THEN: The selected video should be included within the story

title: Split Story Part Text
custom_preconds:
Test URLs:
- https://forge-qa.mlbinfra.com/
- https://forge-opprops-qa.mlbinfra.com/
- https://forge-milb-qa.mlbinfra.com/

Story should be created with text story part
custom_steps: GIVEN: I attempt to split the text within the text story part
custom_expected: THEN: The text story part should be in split into two separate story parts

title: Add Oembed Story Part
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I have created a story
WHEN: I attempt to add an Oembed Story Part
custom_expected: THEN: The Oembed Story Part should be added to the Story

title: Add Photo Story Part
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I have created a story
WHEN: I attempt to add a photo to the story
custom_expected: THEN: The Photo should be added within the Story

title: Style Text via WYSIWYG Editor
custom_preconds:
Test URLs:
- https://forge-qa.mlbinfra.com/
- https://forge-opprops-qa.mlbinfra.com/
- https://forge-milb-qa.mlbinfra.com/

Story should be created already with a text story part
custom_steps: WHEN: I attempt to style the text within the story part
custom_expected: THEN: The text is styled as intended

title: Player Mention
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I have created a story
WHEN: I attempt to mention a Player
custom_expected: THEN: The Player should be mentioned successfully within the story

title: Add Link to a Story
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I have created a story
WHEN: I attempt to add a Link Entity within the story
custom_expected: THEN: The Link Entity should be added within the Story

title: Remove Link in a Story
custom_preconds:
Test URLs:
- https://forge-qa.mlbinfra.com/

A story should be already created with a link entity as a story part

title: Publish Story
custom_steps:
GIVEN: I have created a story
WHEN: I attempt to publish the story
custom_expected: THEN: The story should be successfully published

title: Unpublish Story
custom_preconds:
Test URLs:
- https://forge-qa.mlbinfra.com/
- https://forge-opprops-qa.mlbinfra.com/
- https://forge-milb-qa.mlbinfra.com/

A story should be created
custom_steps:

WHEN: I attempt to unpublish the story
custom_expected: THEN: The story should be unpublished

custom_steps:

custom_steps:

custom_expected: THEN: The story should be archived correctly

custom_steps:

WHEN: I attempt to restore the story
custom_expected: THEN: The story should no longer be archived and should now be unpublished
